{"tid":2410807,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"荷蘭海牙法院撤消政府的「防疫宵禁令」","createTime":"2021-02-17T02:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T23:46:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"02082915ba2d87b4d5b01b784f4276d1e4c5268e","tid":2410807,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:11:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575912-20210216.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575912-20210216.htm&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BRqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=2fc51e51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575912-20210216.htm&h=f5c9ca9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575912-20210216.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n荷蘭海牙一間法院下令政府，立即取消為了控制新型肺炎疫情而實施的宵禁令，認為宵禁令缺乏適當法律依據。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭政府自1月23日起，頒布自二戰以來首次宵禁令，引起不少民眾批評和抗議，有團體向法院挑戰政府的決定，認為當局錯誤地使用緊急權力。<br />\n<br />\n法官認為，政府無清楚解釋為何要在現階段實施宵禁，因為宵禁令生效前，荷蘭國內的感染率已經開始下降，宵禁令嚴重侵犯民眾的行動自由與私隱，裁定宵禁令不合法。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭司法部發言人說，要研究法院的裁決。"},{"pid":"3a3c122b6674563ea4b291f00cbe2dd5bafbd0e4","tid":2410807,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"宵禁令生效前荷蘭國內的感染率已經開始下降，所以唔可以宵禁<br />\n<br />\n歐洲佬仍然係咁樣抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b25fada22e86615b691af99b3cbb536eb62dd2b","tid":2410807,"uid":116960,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a3c122b6674563ea4b291f00cbe2dd5bafbd0e4","tid":2410807,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"宵禁令生效前荷蘭國內的感染率已經開始下降，所以唔可以宵禁<br />\n<br />\n歐洲佬仍然係咁樣抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T02:21:50.000Z","msg":"唔係全世界都要同香港人一樣咁驚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c